the baia mare champions trophy (romanian: trofeul campionilor baia mare) is a pre-season international women's team handball tournament for clubs, held each year in baia mare, romania. the competition is hosted by liga naţională club hcm baia mare and governed by the rules and regulations of the ihf. it is currently contested by six teams. the event, inaugurated in 2014, takes place around a week before the bucharest trophy.